        =\begin{bmatrix}1 \amp a\\0 \amp 1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix}x\\ y \end{bmatrix}
        </me>
        where <m>a>0</m>. Refer to <xref ref="fig_x-postive-shear" /> for <m>a=1/4</m>. <figure
